223
00:12:21,420 --> 00:12:22,470
Send me a photo of them every week.

224
00:12:23,180 --> 00:12:23,830
Once I think they look

225
00:12:23,910 --> 00:12:24,470
similar to the original ones,

226
00:12:24,470 --> 00:12:24,910
