252
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:26,830
I remember you were

253
00:13:26,870 --> 00:13:27,150
fascinated with

254
00:13:27,190 --> 00:13:28,230
the Bermuda Triangle mystery

255
00:13:28,310 --> 00:13:29,150
