258
00:13:32,710 --> 00:13:34,390
Unfortunately I was a step too slow.

259
00:13:34,670 --> 00:13:35,580
I only managed to get the small piece.

260
00:13:36,430 --> 00:13:38,310
This is good enough.

261
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:40,350
I think

262
00:13:40,350 --> 00:13:41,790
I'm just like this meteorite,

263
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:43,270
taking hundred

264
00:13:43,550 --> 00:13:44,790
or thousand millions of light years

265
00:13:45,190 --> 00:13:45,950
to reach the earth.

266
00:13:46,630 --> 00:13:48,150
It's like me taking ten years

267
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,710
to finally be with you.

268
00:13:50,710 --> 00:13:51,190
Thank you.

269
00:13:51,950 --> 00:13:52,830
I really like the gift.

270
00:13:53,950 --> 00:13:55,230
I think they're open now.

271
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:56,150
Let's go.

272
